OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman found dead in caravan
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with a murder investigation
OL,8,Fafter a man was found dead in a
OL,9,Fcaravan.
OL,11,FA 56-year-old man was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of murder, and has since
OL,13,Fbeen released on police bail while
OL,14,Fenquiries continue.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, a second man, aged 42, was
OL,17,Falso arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,18,Fon Wednesday July 8, and is in police
OL,19,Fcustody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
