OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1783633273
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman found dead in caravan
OL,6,FThe death was reported to police on
OL,7,FMonday 6 July at around 11.40pm in
OL,8,FDerby Road, Loughborough.
OL,10,FEast Midlands Ambulance Service
OL,11,Fpronounced a man in his 40s dead at
OL,12,Fthe scene.
OL,14,FOfficers say initial enquiries suggest
OL,15,Fthe deceased man had been involved in
OL,16,Fan altercation in the days before his
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
