PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1783633273
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman found dead in caravan
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Mike Chandler from
OL,7,FLeicestershire Police said they are
OL,8,F"working to understand what's happened
OL,9,Fin this altercation and the events
OL,10,Fthat led to the death of this man.
OL,12,FHe added: "Officers will be in the
OL,13,Farea of Derby Road over the coming
OL,14,Fdays, carrying out enquiries and
OL,15,Fforensic investigations. A cordon will
OL,16,Fremain in place while these enquiries
OL,17,Fare carried out."
